ity of the described methodology for both\ndigital and analog beamforming antenna arrays of different scales and discuss\nits further extension to support real-time operation with dynamic hardware\nimpairments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Jan 2023 19:40:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2023 14:51:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 14:54:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
