dering global and local flame properties in comparison to the DC\nreference data. It is shown that the new FPV model, incorporating large\ncurvature variations in the manifold, leads to improved predictions for the\nmicrostructure of the corrugated flame front and the formation of cellular\nstructures, while global flame properties are reasonably well reproduced by\nboth models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2023 10:14:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-18"}
